wakuang.popItem1ContentText: Holding Tokens to Earn Interest is a tool product created by our company to help users quickly make on-chain pledges and obtain rewards. By staking digital assets on the blockchain network, you can obtain rewards based on the POS (Proof of Stake) mechanism. In this mechanism, users entrust digital assets to nodes, and nodes exercise their rights to produce blocks, package transactions, etc. on the blockchain and receive rewards. Users share the rewards obtained by nodes in proportion to the number of locked positions.
wakuang.popItem1TitleText: What is holding currency to earn interest?
wakuang.popItem2ContentText: Holding the currency to earn interest can obtain relatively stable rewards from third parties, and the product terms are diverse.
wakuang.popItem3ContentText: To earn interest by holding currency is to pledge your digital assets on the blockchain to support the operation of the blockchain network and obtain corresponding rewards.
wakuang.popItem3TitleText: Instructions for investing in interest-earning assets
wakuang.popItem4ContentText: After the subscription is successful on T day, interest will begin at 00:00 on T+1 and interest will be settled at 02:00.
wakuang.popItem5ContentText: Subscription is supported at any time.
wakuang.popItem6ContentText: If you redeem a fixed-term product in advance, the system will deduct part of the income already obtained from the order.
wakuang.rengGouShengQingShengHeZhongTipsText: Your subscription application is under review, please wait patiently
wakuang.secondTitleTipsText: Lock-up mining is to earn mining income in the platform mining pool by entrusting USDT to the platform's super-computing mining machine
wakuang.youshi3Text: Output on the same day after successful lock-up

wakuangList.popItem1ContentText: Pledge mining is a tool product created by the company to help users quickly stake on the chain to obtain rewards. By staking digital assets on the blockchain network, and obtaining rewards based on the POS (Proof of Stake) mechanism. In this mechanism, users entrust digital assets to nodes, and nodes exercise rights such as producing blocks and packaging transactions on the blockchain and receive rewards. Users share the rewards obtained by nodes in proportion to the number of locked positions.
wakuangList.popItem2ContentText: Staking mining can obtain relatively stable third-party rewards, and the product term is diverse.
wakuangList.popItem3ContentText: Pledge mining is to pledge your digital assets on the blockchain to support the operation of the blockchain network and obtain corresponding rewards.
wakuangList.popItem4ContentText: After successful subscription on T day, the interest rate will start at 00:00 on T+1 day, and the interest will be settled at 02:00.
wakuangList.popItem5ContentText: Subscription is supported at any time.
wakuangList.popItem6ContentText: If you redeem a regular product in advance, the system will deduct part of the income already obtained from the order.
